Origin

The man known as Astrolabe is actually named Al-Hasan. He was a human member of a group known as The Guardians in the year 1000. Astrolabe holds a sentient star inside his mind.

Creation

Astrolabe was created by Dan Abnett and Carlo Barberi and first appeared in Guardians of Infinity issue 1 (2016).

Major Story Arcs

Meeting the Guardians from 21st Century

Astrolabe and his group of Guardians met their twentyfirst counterparts in a battle for the ages.

deck: The fickle specter of crime
description:
Origin

Lady Crime is a pale red garbed specter of crime that finds those contemplating a life of crime and encourages them to do commit their first one, she then egress and even possesses them for brief moments to commit worse and more criminal acts. When the perpetrators are finally arrested she disappears. While egging them on they are the only ones who can see and hear Lady Crime.

Creator

Created by Bob Powell, Lady Crime only made one appearance, however she was brought back in 1992 by AC for a one-shot that reprinted her only story and put her in as the narrator of two other Bob Powell crime stories.
name: Lady Crime
